TenantSecurityLoginIpRangeTrend.name: TenantSecurityLoginIpRangeTrend
TenantSecurityLoginIpRangeTrend.description: Stores details of changes related to login IP ranges in Security Center.

Action.description: The type of change made to the login IP range. Possible values are: ADDED REMOVED UPDATED

ActionBy.description: The name of the person who made this change.

ActionDate.description: The timestamp for when this change was made.

Description.description: The description of the login IP range record.

DetailIdentifier.description: The unique identifier for this detail record.

IpEndAddress.description: The end IP address of the login IP range. For example, 10.0.0.0 – 10.255.255.255.

IpRangeIdentifier.description: Unique identifier of the IP range.

IpStartAddress.description: The start IP address of the login IP range. For example, 10.0.0.0 – 10.255.255.255.

MetricIdentifier.description: The ID of the corresponding TenantSecurityMonitorMetric.

MetricsType.description: The type of metric for the data collected.

Name.description: The name of the metric for the data collected.

ProfileIdentifier.description: The ID of the profile that is assigned to this login IP range.

ProfileName.description: The name of the profile that is assigned to this login IP range.

Tenant.description: The ID of the tenant (org) that this record is for.

TenantName.description: The name of the tenant (org) that this record is for.
